name: Ohio State vs Mi State
summary: On Saturday night under the lights at Spartan Stadium, the Michigan State Spartans hosted the third-ranked Ohio State Buckeyes. The game was highly anticipated, with both teams looking to make a statement in the Big Ten standings. Unfortunately for the Spartans, Ohio State proved to be too much, pulling away for a 38-7 victory. The Buckeyes offense was led by quarterback C.J. Stroud, who threw for 265 yards and four touchdowns. Running back TreVeyon Henderson added 118 yards rushing and a touchdown. The Spartans offense struggled to find a rhythm, mustering just 185 yards of total offense, including negative 16 rushing yards. The loss drops Michigan State to 2-3 on the season, while Ohio State improves to 5-0.

summary: Drake Hogestyn, the veteran actor known for his portrayal of John Black on the long-running soap opera "Days of Our Lives," passed away at the age of 70. Hogestyn's death was confirmed by several entertainment publications, including Soap Opera Digest, Variety, TheWrap, Deadline, and PEOPLE. According to PEOPLE, Hogestyn succumbed to pancreatic cancer, which was the cause of his demise. The news of Hogestyn's passing has shocked and saddened fans and colleagues alike, as he was a beloved figure in the soap opera community.
